test.out
2D Frame linear static analysis
LinearStatic nsteps 1 nmodules 1
errorcheck
domain 2dBeam
OutputManager tstep_all dofman_all element_all
ndofman 4 nelem 3 ncrosssect 3 nmat 1 nbc 7 nic 0 nltf 1 nset 10
#Nodes
node 1 coords 3  0  0.0  0
node 2 coords 3  0  0.0  4
node 3 coords 3  5  0.0  4
node 4 coords 3  5  0.0  0
#Beams
Beam2d 1   nodes 2    1 2
Beam2d 2   nodes 2    4 3
Beam2d 3   nodes 2    2 3    dofstocondense 1 3
#Sections
SimpleCS 1  area 0.002   Iz 2e-05   beamShearCoeff 1.e30  material 1  set 1
SimpleCS 2  area 0.002   Iz 2e-05   beamShearCoeff 1.e30  material 1  set 2
SimpleCS 3  area 0.002   Iz 2e-05   beamShearCoeff 1.e30  material 1  set 3
#Material
IsoLE 1 d 1.  E 210000000000.0  n 0.3  tAlpha 1.2e-5
#Boundary conditions
NodalLoad 1 loadTimeFunction 1 dofs 1 3 Components 1 -5000 set 4
BoundaryCondition 2 loadTimeFunction 1 dofs 1 1 values 1 0. set 5
BoundaryCondition 3 loadTimeFunction 1 dofs 1 1 values 1 0. set 6
BoundaryCondition 4 loadTimeFunction 1 dofs 1 3 values 1 0. set 7
BoundaryCondition 5 loadTimeFunction 1 dofs 1 3 values 1 0. set 8
BoundaryCondition 6 loadTimeFunction 1 dofs 1 5 values 1 0. set 9
BoundaryCondition 7 loadTimeFunction 1 dofs 1 5 values 1 0. set 10
ConstantFunction 1 f(t) 1.
#Sets
Set 1 elementranges {(1 1)}
Set 2 elementranges {(2 2)}
Set 3 elementranges {(3 3)}
Set 4 nodes 1 3
Set 5 nodes 1 1
Set 6 nodes 1 4
Set 7 nodes 1 1
Set 8 nodes 1 4
Set 9 nodes 1 1
Set 10 nodes 1 4
